		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Starting at 17th level, you nearly reach the highest peak of the mysteries your element offers you. Choose one benefit from the following:</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Elemental Security</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You have certain immunities, determined by your archetype spell list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Fire Priest. </strong>Immunity to fire damage and effects.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Ice Priest. </strong>Immunity to cold damage and effects.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Plant Priest.</strong> Immune to poison damage, the poisoned condition, as well as spells and effects from the plant school.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Stone Priest. </strong>Immune to force damage and effects.&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Storm Priest. </strong>Immune to lightning and thunder damage, and storm effects.&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Water Priest.</strong> Immune to acid damage and water effects. You also can also breathe underwater, and you gain a swim speed equal to your base walking speed. If you already have a swim speed, it instead increases by 30 feet.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Elemental Freedom</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You have a flying speed equal to your walking speed.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
